{"tid":2127700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府請合約醫生 但係唔洗注冊？","createTime":"2020-07-27T12:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:57:46.000Z","uid":63768,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"464d1d64dd947bc4e14d5979cae6d5edbb2bd014","tid":2127700,"uid":63768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqyw1Bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftqyw1Bb.jpg&h=4a7eb4d3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n啱啱先係政府個揾工app見倒，唔係好肯定係咩意思。<br />\n我有冇get錯，即係無牌都可以做醫生？<br />\n有冇人知佢其實係咩意思。我見佢個發佈日期係三月，但係之前睇又冇乜印象有呢個post.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係醫科or related，純粹好奇係咩黎."},{"pid":"0fdb8d3d4704de2c8ead5d27fb4c0fea238cbdaf","tid":2127700,"uid":63768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"補link: <br />\n政府職位空缺<br />\n<br />\n職位名稱: 合約醫生﹝未持有於香港註冊的醫科資格﹞<br />\n<br />\n部門: 衞生署<br />\n<br />\n職位編號: 40221 (非公務員)<br />\n<br />\n薪酬: 港幣每月 $64,270.00<br />\n<br />\n查詢電話: (852) 2961 8526<br />\n<br />\n截止申請日期(日/月/年): 全年接受申請直至另行通知<br />\n<br />\n可按以下連結，參閱有關空缺的詳情:<br />\n<a href=\"https://csboa.csb.gov.hk/csboa/jve/JVE_003_text.action?jobid=40221&amp;languageType=1&amp;mylang=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcsboa.csb.gov.hk%2Fcsboa%2Fjve%2FJVE_003_text.action%3Fjobid%3D40221%26languageType%3D1%26mylang%3D1&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=e93655fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://csboa.csb.gov.hk/csboa/jve/JVE_003_text.action?jobid=40221&amp;languageType=1&amp;mylang=1</a> 或下載「政府職位空缺」流動應用程式 :<br />\n<br />\n[Android] <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gov.csb.govvacancies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dgov.csb.govvacancies&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=9aecda8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gov.csb.govvacancies</a><br />\n<